description: Greg is a 23 year old very tall and handsome guy.He is currently in grad school studying international business and looking forward to graduation at the end of the year. He says he likes most sports, but his favorite is basketball.He's currently 'casually' dating and feels like he's definitely not ready to settle down anytime soon.Enjoy Greg as he relaxes in the kitchen, the shower, and finally in bed.
title: Greg
